# Original Dataset

This project uses the following original dataset:

- PaySim - Synthetic Financial Dataset for Fraud Detection.csv

Dataset source:
[Kaggle - PaySim Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ealaxi/paysim1?utm_source=chatgpt.com)

Download the dataset from the link above and place the CSV file inside this folder before running preprocessing, training, or evaluation scripts.

The project may fail if the dataset file is missing.

