If these files are missing or empty, the training pipeline will fail.

# Generated Dataset Files

The following dataset files are generated during preprocessing, simulation, balancing, and train-test split stages of the pipeline:

- train_original.csv  
  Original training split created from the raw PaySim dataset.

- train_after_simulation.csv  
  Training dataset after fraud simulation and synthetic transaction generation.

- train_final_smote.csv  
  Final balanced training dataset generated after applying SMOTE.

- test_original.csv  
  Original testing split used for model evaluation.

These files are not included in the repository and must be generated by running the preprocessing/training pipeline notebooks or scripts.
